					<description><![CDATA[In reply to &lt;a href=&quot;https://wordcounter.net/blog/2016/10/05/102258_using-a-pseudonym.html#comments/11559&quot;&gt;Liniol&lt;/a&gt;.

That&#039;s a ridiculous statement. There are many reasons for using a pseudonym and it is up to the individual as to why they make that choice. No one has the right to make a negative comment about an individual&#039;s choices about why they make this decision. If it is not harming anyone, then keep your views to yourself and try to write a successful book yourself. I can tell you, it&#039;s an incredible experience but very hard work!]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In reply to <a href="https://wordcounter.net/blog/2016/10/05/102258_using-a-pseudonym.html#comments/11559">Liniol</a>.</p>
<p>That&#8217;s a ridiculous statement. There are many reasons for using a pseudonym and it is up to the individual as to why they make that choice. No one has the right to make a negative comment about an individual&#8217;s choices about why they make this decision. If it is not harming anyone, then keep your views to yourself and try to write a successful book yourself. I can tell you, it&#8217;s an incredible experience but very hard work!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
